definition: classifier indicating a small amount or small number greater than 1: some, a few, several

sentences.english: Some other drugs have to be taken on an empty stomach.
sentences.chinese: 而其他某些药物，必须在空腹服用。

sentences.english: Father Mabeuf was one of those persons for whom plants have souls.
sentences.chinese: 和某些人一样，马白夫公公也认为植物是有灵魂的。

sentences.english: Or, at least some prominent figures think so.
sentences.chinese: 至少某些知名人士是这样认为的。

sentences.english: GRBs come from some of the most energetic explosions known in the Universe.
sentences.chinese: GRBs来自宇宙中某些最高能量的爆炸。

sentences.english: His work partakes of the aesthetic fashions of his time.
sentences.chinese: 他的作品具有当时的某些审美时尚。

sentences.english: And certain high-risk professions and hobbies usually have to be disclosed.
sentences.chinese: 某些高风险职业和业余爱好通常也必须予以说明澄清。

sentences.english: Some high level but defined quality standards must be put in place.
sentences.chinese: 某些高级但是确定的质量标准必须就位。

sentences.english: Some of your people will also need to bedismissed because of excessive absenteeism.
sentences.chinese: 你的某些员工，经常旷工，因而也需要被开除。

sentences.english: Some of them skip classes just because they have no interest in certain subjects.
sentences.chinese: 有的跳班仅仅是因为他们没有在某些科目的兴趣。

sentences.english: Some surgeries and drugs could lead to the sphincter of Oddi dysfunction.
sentences.chinese: 某些外科手术或药物会引起奥狄氏括约肌机能障碍。

sentences.english: In the opinion of some lofty experts they never quite cohered again.
sentences.chinese: 在某些玄虚的专家看来，他们没有再完全融洽统一过。

sentences.english: Certain other expenses also may be deducted from taxable income, or one may elect to use the "standard deduction.
sentences.chinese: 某些其他支出也可从应缴纳的个人收入税中扣除。

sentences.english: Some of the pixel formats contain premultiplied color values.
sentences.chinese: 某些像素格式包含自左乘的颜色值。

sentences.english: A seemingly inflexible adherence to specific, nonfunctional routines or rituals
sentences.chinese: 僵化地坚持某些特定，非功能性的生活习惯或仪式。

sentences.english: Rivers and lakes might dry up in some places, and glaciers might melt.
sentences.chinese: 某些地方的河川跟湖泊可能干涸，冰河也可能溶化。

definition: some/a few/a little/(following an adjective) slightly ...er
(used for abstract things) a good deal, a lot of
this/this kind of/this sort of/this type of
other/the others/else/other than it/in addition to the thing mentioned above
